prix.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d4e08b9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d4e08b9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h1>Brunch le Week-End<\/h1><p>Les samedis et dimanches, de 10h30 \u00e0 14h30, c\u2019est brunch time !<\/p><p>Au programme : viennoiseries, granola maison, tartines \u0153uf bacon, tartines avocat \u0153uf, et toujours nos c\u00e9l\u00e8bres club sandwichs shokupan. Quelques plats et desserts maison compl\u00e8tent l\u2019offre, sans oublier nos irr\u00e9sistibles cookies, brookies, brownies, et carrot cakes.<\/p><p>Venez passer un bon moment dans une ambiance cool et d\u00e9tendue !<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eb5fe05 e-con-full e-flex wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no wpr-column-slider-no wpr-equal-height-no e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"eb5fe05\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a1f16e4 e-con-full e-flex wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no wpr-column-slider-no wpr-equal-height-no e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a1f16e4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-262f5d6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"262f5d6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/petite-pension.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/image00884-768x1024.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2282\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/petite-pension.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/image00884-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https: